</disciplines><abstract>&lt;p&gt;Perhaps the aspect of all our lives undergoing the most transition in current times is the workplace. Gone seemingly forever is the time when you started working for an organization, company, or institution of higher education and had an excellent chance of working there for 30, 40, or more years if you so chose. This paper describes how distance education can reach people who are undergoing workplace transition.&lt;/p&gt;</abstract>
